com.snapbundle.builder

Class ExtensionBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.snapbundle.builder.ExtensionBuilder

  • public final class ExtensionBuilder
extends Object
    Convenience Builder pattern class for creating new IExtension instances.

    The minimum fields required to define a new instance are:

    • Field.NAME_FIELD
    • Field.DESCRIPTION_FIELD
    • Field.LONG_DESCRIPTION_FIELD
    • Field.REDIRECT_URL_FIELD
    • Field.EXTENSION_TYPE_FIELD
    • Field.SUPPORT_EMAIL_FIELD
    • Field.WEB_SITE_FIELD
